    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Pytz Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Pytz</application> library brings the IANA tz database
        into Python. It allows accurate and cross-platform timezone
        calculations.
      </para>

      &lfs122_checked;

